Guess 8: covers 4,9,12,6. After four guesses, are all rectangles covered? Let's list all covered rectangles: From guess 2: 1,4,8,11. From guess 4: 2,5,7,10. From guess 6: 5,6,8,9,12. From guess 8: 4,6,9,12. Now, compiling all covered rectangles: 1,4,8,11,2,5,7,10,5,6,8,9,12,4,6,9
